article.headline: Timmerman's 16 help Winthrop down Toccoa Falls 113-62
article.description: — Alex Timmerman's 16 points helped Winthrop defeat Toccoa Falls 113-62 on Friday night.
article.linkText: Timmerman's 16 help Winthrop down Toccoa Falls 113-62
article.story: ROCK HILL, S.C. -- — Alex Timmerman's 16 points helped Winthrop defeat Toccoa Falls 113-62 on Friday night. Timmerman also contributed five rebounds for the Eagles (9-6). Yoro Diallo scored 14 points and added 12 rebounds. Xavier McKelvy had 13 points and was 4 of 9 shooting, including 1 for 4 from 3-point range, and went 4 for 4 from the line. The Screaming Eagles were led by Josh Parker, who posted 21 points and six assists. Anthony Williams II added 20 points for Toccoa Falls. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
